# Launching a new instance

To do this, set up an account with amazon AWS (Amazon Web Services). 

In the market place choice, this tutorial assumes debian is chosen. Follow the steps below. 

Open the Amazon EC2 console at https://console.aws.amazon.com/ec2/.

From the console dashboard, click Launch Instance.
